pi-stomp (3.0-15) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Footswitch preset switches: show the snapshot name on the label and light
    the LCD indicator for the active snapshot.
  * Footswitch preset bindings no longer leak across pedalboard loads.
  * Plugin panels can now render as non-fullscreen dialogs.
  * New plugin panels: CAPS Noisegate, DISTRHO Compressor, Reverb (with mode
    selector), GX Cabinet.
  * More EQ plugin types (parametric, graphic, custom).
  * Window decorations use analytic curves for consistent visuals.
  * Analytic rounded edges for dialogs.
  * Plugin windows match the visual style of regular windows.
  * Plugin window UI consistent with menus; vertical centering for large dialogs.
  * Analog controls aligned to pedal columns.
  * (v3) Fix plugin panels not refreshing bypass on main screen.
  * Quicker, less aggressive subtitle.
  * Fix non-idempotent plugin tile renders.
  * Fix dirty corner invalidation.

 -- Cam Gorrie <sastraxi@gmail.com>  Thu, 02 Jul 2026 22:30:00 -0400

